<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/wzxinchen/Blazui">wzxinchen/Blazui: Element的blazor版本，用 .NET 写前端的 UI 框架，无JS，无TS，非 Silverlight，非 WebForm，开箱即用</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/ant-design-blazor/ant-design-blazor/">ant-design-blazor/ant-design-blazor: 🌈A set of enterprise-class UI components based on Ant Design and Blazor WebAssembly.</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

